{subhead}AmigaDE Party Pack Announcement{def}
{left}
{pp}
Greetings to members of the Amiga Family.  Wow, what a year it has been!
In the coming weeks we are going to see the releases of not one but three new Amiga Products!:
{pp}
AmigaOne PPC /1200 - On Schedule and Rockin'
{pp}
AmigaOS 4.0, and shortly thereafter AmigaOS 4.2 on schedule for release Summer of '01 and will 
offer the next generation of Amiga desktop - on PPC!
{pp}
AmigaDE 1.1 so the rest of the world may begin to learn the power of Amiga - For Cell Phones, 
PDA's, and other portable devices.
{pp}
Because of overwhelming e-mails and suggestions Amiga Incorporated is pleased to announce the 
AmigaOne, AmigaOS 4.0, AmigaOS 4.2, and AmigaDE pre-release party!
{pp}
Here is how you can participate at this party:
{pp}
Starting June 11th and ending June 22nd 2001 Amiga Family members can purchase a pre-
release version of AmigaDE for 99.00, you will receive one year of updates, the SDK, a bundle of
sample applications and games, and the ability to start using DE on Windows or Linux desktops.
This offer is available on-line from the AmigaMall or from your Amiga dealer.
{pp}
Next you can pick from either a 100.00 discount coupon on an AmigaONE PPC/1200 for use at
your local dealer, or you can receive AmigaOS 4.0 and 4.2 (when available) for FREE!
That's right, until June 22nd only purchase the pre-release of AmigaDE, get the SDK, and all the
trimmings and select either a 100.00 off a new AmigaONE, or AmigaOS 4.0 and 4.2 (when
available) for FREE.
{pp}
It is your choice and it is available today at The AmigaMall! or your local Amiga dealer.
{pp}
-Amiga
{pp}